OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780344353
OL,3,CMan dies after being rescued from
OL,4,CBalderton Lake in Newark
OL,6,FA man has died after being rescued
OL,7,Ffrom Balderton Lake near Newark
OL,8,Fearlier this week (Thursday 28 May).
OL,10,FNottinghamshire Police,
OL,11,FNottinghamshire Fire and Rescue
OL,12,FService, and East Midlands Ambulance
OL,13,FService attended the scene and a 19-
OL,14,Fyear-old man was recovered from the
OL,15,Fwater.
OL,17,FHe had been at the lake with friends
OL,18,Fand was treated at the scene by
OL,19,Fparamedics and then taken to hospital.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
