PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780344353
OL,3,CMan dies after being rescued from
OL,4,CBalderton Lake in Newark
OL,6,FPolice say the man's death is not
OL,7,Fthought to be suspicious and that a
OL,8,Ffile will be prepared for the coroner.
OL,10,FClive Collings, Chief Inspector for
OL,11,FNewark from Nottinghamshire Police
OL,12,Fsaid: "This is a tragic incident and
OL,13,Four thoughts are solely with this
OL,14,Fyoung man's family.
OL,16,F"We recognise this will be very
OL,17,Fupsetting for the local community and
OL,18,Fwe encourage people to access support
OL,19,Fif they need it.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780344353
OL,3,CMan dies after being rescued from
OL,4,CBalderton Lake in Newark
OL,6,F"During hot weather we know people
OL,7,Fwant to keep cool but open waters are
OL,8,Fexceptionally dangerous as there is no
OL,9,Fway of telling what's beneath the
OL,10,Fsurface."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
