CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780344353
OL,3,CMan dies after being rescued from
OL,4,CBalderton Lake in Newark
OL,6,FGroup Manager Charlotte Weatherall-
OL,7,FSmith from Nottinghamshire Fire and
OL,8,FRescue Service said, "On behalf of
OL,9,FNottinghamshire Fire and Rescue
OL,10,FService, I would like to extend our
OL,11,Fdeepest sympathies and heartfelt
OL,12,Fcondolences to the family, friends and
OL,13,Floved ones of this young man at this
OL,14,Fincredibly difficult time. This is a
OL,15,Ftragic incident, and our thoughts
OL,16,Fremain with everyone affected.
OL,26,@pD@VOU
