PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780344353
OL,3,CMan dies after being rescued from
OL,4,CBalderton Lake in Newark
OL,6,F"Incidents like this are a stark
OL,7,Freminder of the dangers that open
OL,8,Fwater can present. Even on warm and
OL,9,Fsunny days, water temperatures can be
OL,10,Fmuch colder than they appear, and
OL,11,Fentering the water can lead to cold
OL,12,Fwater shock, which can be sudden,
OL,13,Fsevere and potentially fatal.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
