OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780344353
OL,3,CMan dies after being rescued from
OL,4,CBalderton Lake in Newark
OL,6,F"If you see someone in difficulty in
OL,7,Fthe water, call 999 immediately and
OL,8,Fask for the fire service. Encourage
OL,9,Fthe person to float on their back to
OL,10,Fhelp them stay calm and conserve
OL,11,Fenergy. For your own safety, please do
OL,12,Fnot enter the water or attempt a
OL,13,Frescue yourself, as this can put
OL,14,Fadditional lives at risk.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
